{{ tffile "examples/provider/provider_auth.tf" }}

### Environment Variables

Credentials can be provided by using the `KRAFTCLOUD_TOKEN` environment
variable. The KraftCloud metro can be set using the `KRAFTCLOUD_METRO`
environment variable.

Usage:

```terraform
provider "kraftcloud" {}
```

```sh
export KRAFTCLOUD_TOKEN='cm9ib3QkbXl1c2VyLnVuaWtyYWZ0LmlvLnVzZXJzLmtyYWZ0Y2xvdWQ6a1I0ZjdFWEFNUExFS0VZ'
```

```sh
export KRAFTCLOUD_METRO='fra0'
```

